title: The.Taste.of.Success.S01E01.HDTV.XviD-spinzes.avi
description:
Tayto, Ballymaloe, Donegal Catch -- all tasty Irish food products that we couldn't imagine a world without, but there are still plenty of foodies on this island of ours that would like to add to that. The Taste of Success is all about Irish food producers competing to win a 100,000 euro prize and see their item on supermarket shelves.




The Taste of Success - Series 1, Episode 1



Episode 1 kicks off with Catherine Fulvio showcasing the best of Leinster. So be prepared to meet wild forager Mary with her Beech Leaf Liquer, novice baker Eleanor has a great gluten free bread and Sharon creates a honey alternative with her Dandelion Flower Preserve. 8 contestants show their wares but 4 will be going home after tonight. Who will be in line to win The Taste of Success?



Original Air Date: 21-Oct-2014
